dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alexander Morgan. May I have your name, please?
Hi Alexander, my name is Lori Wright.
Nice to meet you, Lori. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight zero two three four and my date of birth is zero four / one two / one nine eight six.
Thank you, Lori. One final piece of information required for security reasons, could you provide the make and model of your vehicle?
Of course, I drive a Toyota Camry.
Thank you for providing the information, Lori. Is there anything specific you'd like to inquire about or discuss regarding your insurance policy today?
I wanted to confirm my premium payment date for this month.
I can assist you with that, Lori. Your premium payment is due on the twenty-fifth of this month. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance.
Thank you for your time, Lori. Have a great day.
